results.title: Personalized Wood Slice Sign, Love Wood Sign, Live Love Laugh Sign, Cheers Sign, Welcome Sign, Wood Slice Sign, Engraved Wood Round Sign
results.description:
Our beautiful personalized sign are made from authentic and quality pine wood slices.  Choose between 4 different styles that we at Timeless Designing will gladly bring to life.  Our signs are carefully laser engraved with design of your choice.  They're then sealed with mineral oil to help protect against staining and to create some water resistance.  (We recommend reapplying mineral oil every 6 months to guarantee protection).  Because these are real pine slices with bark, some bark may fall off.

Our pine sign is perfect for any gift whether for a holiday, wedding, housewarming, special event, birthday, and especially for an anniversary.  They're 10 inches in diameter and approximately 0.75 inches thick.  You can add on a sawtooth hanger to the back of the sign for easy hanging, for an additional cost.

Your sign will arrive neatly wrapped in a ribbon.

If you would like a custom order go to https://www.etsy.com/listing/930484996/custom-wood-sign-wooden-table-piece?ref=listing_published_alert

Personalized note included along with instructions on how to care for your product.
